data.description: What an opportunity! This historic farmhouse features 3 bedrooms, a spacious first-floor bathroom, hardwood flooring throughout, a heat pump, pellet stove, and an attached barn that could be made into more living space or used as-is for storage. The home sits on a quiet street and has a TON of potential. This would make an excellent first time home for someone, OR an investment/flip opportunity for an investor. The possibilities are endless!
